{
  "stem": "1975.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 81.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, in the morning, when the sun came out, we start moving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we moved like in a-- in a way that we were one behind the other one, was about a few feet away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We should not be together, considered together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we walked through the day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we tried to avoid-- we tried to walk out from the city and to go towards [NON-ENGLISH], which was a forest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of us, this Fin, knew the neighborhood because he used to live in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he know exactly where we were going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Plus the fact that we knew that there were some partisans, some freedom fighters in the vicinity.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When we came to a point, it was already towards the other half in the afternoon, we came to a point where we had to cross a main highway.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was a very dangerous point because there was movement of Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Germans wouldn't know the distinguish between Jew and non-Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Plus the fact we didn't have way-- we actually-- they could have spotted us in the face.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we tried to camouflage ourselves in a certain way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But some of the Lithuanians with a-- two of them, one of them was with a-- with a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the other one was on foot and they had their rifles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one of them came over and they saw us and said, documents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When he said that, we were already outside of the city.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We just disbanded and start running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This guy with a rifle was not able to shoot towards-- so he pointed the one apparently he had one-- this guy that was from Poland.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we lost each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, we didn't know-- I didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
